Title: The Bridge
Writer: Margaret Atwood (based on the novel by), Nina Fiore (executive story editor), John Hererra (executive story editor), Bruce Miller (created by), Eric Tuchman
Actors: Elisabeth Moss, Joseph Fiennes, Yvonne Strahovski, Madeline Brewer
Plot: June is tasked with going back to Jezebels to find a package. Meanwhile in Gilead, Janine has trouble relinquishing her newborn baby.
